parcel.description:
元宇宙有意识形态吗？设想在元宇宙发展进程的某一阶段，人类与AI终于站在了完全对立的两面，于是人类再度操起了政治与舆论的独门绝学，所有口号、标语、社交媒体上的签名，铺天盖地而来化为“大字报”。我们在此呈现这一架空背景的景观，站在哪一边，交由观众全权决定。

Does Metaverse have ideology ? Imagine at certain time of Metaverse’s  development, human beings are finally on the opposite side of AI. Will human use conventional propaganda methods to manipulate the public opinions?. By presenting this imagined scene, this artwork aims to discuss the existence of ideology in Metaverse, and leave the decision right to audience.
parcel.name: 元宇宙大字报 Meta Dazibao
parcel.label: gallery
